{
 "cells": [
  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "# gaudin-CG working notebook\n\nMathematica notebook for the `gaudin-CG` project. No physics content yet: `paper/gaudinCG.tex` is still just a title and an empty introduction, so there is nothing to check against here. This notebook will grow alongside the paper.",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "ClearAll[f, res1, res0];\nf[u_, n_, S1_, S2_, w_] := Exp[w u] u^n / ((u - 1)^S1 u^S2);\nres1[n_, S1_, S2_] :=res1[n,S1,S2]=Exp[w] LaguerreL[S1 - 1, n - S2 - S1 + 1, -w];\nres0[n_, S1_, S2_] :=res0[n,S1,S2]= If[S2 > n, (-1)^(S1 + S2 - n + 1) LaguerreL[S2 - n - 1, 1 - S1 - S2 + n, w], 0];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "## Residue checks: res1, res0 vs. direct residues of f\n\nCompare `res1`/`res0` against `Residue[f[u,n,S1,S2,w], {u,1}]` / `{u,0}` for `n ∈ {0,...,4}`, `S2 ∈ {0,...,4}`, `S1 ∈ {1,...,4}` (S1=0 means no pole at u=1; `res1` has no guard for that case, unlike `res0`'s `If[S2>n,...,0]`).",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "mismatches1 = Reap[\n   Do[\n    diff = Simplify[res1[n, S1, S2] - Residue[f[u, n, S1, S2, w], {u, 1}]];\n    If[diff =!= 0, Sow[{n, S1, S2, diff}]],\n    {n, 0, 4}, {S1, 1, 4}, {S2, 0, 4}\n    ]\n   ][[2]] // Flatten[#, 1] &;\nLength[mismatches1]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"50770\" data-output-id=\"2\" data-out-n=\"9\" data-sub-idx=\"1\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"3\" data-sub-start=\"7\" data-sub-end=\"7\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[9]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrggat1l-gt91pbk\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"MA==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[9]= 0",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "66274b42-9cf8-449c-9e77-d69cd2e63b61"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "mismatches0 = Reap[\n   Do[\n    diff = Simplify[res0[n, S1, S2] - Residue[f[u, n, S1, S2, w], {u, 0}]];\n    If[diff =!= 0, Sow[{n, S1, S2, diff}]],\n    {n, 0, 4}, {S1, 0, 4}, {S2, 0, 4}\n    ]\n   ][[2]] // Flatten[#, 1] &;\nLength[mismatches0]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
